Frecia: Oh, sorry, just a little thing before you go.  #line:ch3_FairyForest_93


===
title: ch3_e1_FairyForest_3_11
tags:
---
Frecia: Heir to the Blood of the Brave, I apologize for being late to thank you… Thank you for being with Emma.  #line:ch3_FairyForest_94
Frecia: How was Emma doing when she left the fairy forest?  #line:ch3_FairyForest_95

===
title: ch3_e1_FairyForest_3_12
tags:
---
Frecia: Well...good. Emma was not able to achieve her full potential as a fairy here with us. Ironically, I think that by leaving this fairy forest, this child has been able to act like a fairy in her own right....  #line:ch3_FairyForest_96
Frecia:I am sure that it is some kind of fate, or perhaps it is karma, that you, a human being, and not me, the chief of the fairy forest, saved this child...For that I thank you.  #line:ch3_FairyForest_97
===
title: ch3_e1_FairyForest_3_12_2
tags:
---
Frescia: The Fairy Forest code doesn't allow it, but... Emma, I'm so happy to see your face looking so well.  #line:ch3_FairyForest_98

Emma: Thank.. Thank you very much! I, too, was happy to see Lady Frecia's face again!  #line:ch3_FairyForest_99

Frecia: You, too, Werewolf, please take good care of Emma!  #line:ch3_FairyForest_100


Bravo: Oh, I got it! I'm the most useful werewolf there is!   #line:ch3_FairyForest_101
Bravo: Everyone mistakes me for a dog, but you're one of the few that can figure me out! You are indeed a great person!  #line:ch3_FairyForest_102

Emma: Hey, Bravo! Don't talk to Lady Frecia like that!  #line:ch3_FairyForest_103

Bravo: Don't get mad at me for giving her a compliment!  #line:ch3_FairyForest_104

Emma: You have a funny way of complimenting her! Why are you talking like that, you!  #line:ch3_FairyForest_105


Frecia: Hmmm...I'm so glad you're surrounded by reliable friends. I guess I don't have to worry about you anymore.  #line:ch3_FairyForest_106
Frecia:I'm sorry for keeping you then. I have just enchanted the path from the loophole Rose made here to allow you all to access the Fairy Forest...So rest assured, you can use that path for a while.  #line:ch3_FairyForest_107

